    <h1>SLA (Service Level Agreement)</h1>
    <p class="description">A formal contract defining the minimum performance standards, response times, and remedies a service provider must meet. In marketing, SLAs govern <strong>lead response commitments, agency deliverables, and content turnaround times</strong> — the agreements that turn aspirational goals into enforceable standards.</p>
